entries.meaning: (horticulture) After the development of buds and leaves on an apple tree, but before the pink coloration appears.
examples: The apple trees were to receive no dormant lime sulphur, but an application of Scalecide 1 to 15 at the delayed dormant, followed by a prepink lime sulphur 1 to 30 and the pink lime sulphur 1 to 10.
